ire.gov.uk/cms/public-site/schools Schools], [[Oxfordshire County Council]]\n\n{{Schools in Oxfordshire}}\n{{Oxfordshire}}\n{{Schools in England}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:List Of Schools In Oxfordshire}}\n[[Category:Lists of schools in South East England|Oxfordshire]]\n[[Category:Schools in Oxfordshire]]\n[[Category:Lists of buildings and structures in Oxfordshire]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2017}}\n{{Use British English|date=June 2017}}\nThis is a '''list of schools in [[Oxfordshire]]''', [[England]].<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www2.oxfordshire.gov.uk/cms/schools/list/all | title=Schools list | publisher=[[Oxfordshire County Council]] | location=UK | accessdate=5 April 2020 }}</ref> Note that \"CE\" indicates a [[Church of England]] school.\n\n==State-funded schools==\n\n===Primary schools===\n{{Div col|colwidth=30em}}\n*Aston Rowant [[Church of England|CE]] School, [[Aston Rowant]]\n*Barley Hill Primary School, [[Thame]]\n*Bayard's Hill Primary School, [[Oxford]]\n*Berinsfield School, [[Berinsfield]]\n*Botley School, [[Oxford]]\n*Brightwell-cum-Sotwell CE Primary School, [[Brightwell-cum-Sotwell]]\n*Caldecott Primary School, [[Abingdon-on-Thames]]\n*Carswell County Primary School, [[Abingdon-on-Thames]]\n*Carterton County Primary School, [[Carterton, Oxfordshire|Carterton]]\n*Charlbury Primary School, [[Charlbury]]\n*Charlton Primary School, [[Wantage]]\n*Chiltern Edge, [[Sonning Common]]\n*Church Cowley St James Primary School, [[Oxford]]\n*Cumnor CE School, [[Cumnor]]\n*Cutteslowe Primary School, [[Oxford]]\n*Dr Radcliffe's CE Primary School, [[Steeple Aston]]\n*Drayton Primary School, [[Drayton, Vale of White Horse|Drayton]]\n*Dunmore Primary School, [[Abingdon-on-Thames]]\n*East Oxford Primary School, [[Oxford]]\n*Edith Moorhouse Primary School, [[Carterton, Oxfordshire|Carterton]]\n*[[European School, Culham|European School]], [[Culham]]\n*Faringdon Infant School, [[Faringdon]]\n*Faringdon Junior School