aux\n| Episode: \"The Coldest Night of the Year\"\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[Becker (TV series)|Becker]]''\n| Father Joe D'Andrea\n| Episode: \"Crosstalk\"\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[Teacher's Pet (TV series)|Teacher's Pet]]''\n| Narrator / Tim Tim Tim\n| Voice role; episode: #1.12\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[Nature (TV series)|Nature]]''\n| Narrator\n| Episode: \"Intimate Enemies: Lions and Buffalo\"\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''[[Gary the Rat]]''\n| Steele\n| Voice role; episode: \"Strange Bedfellows\"\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''Fathers and Sons''\n| Gene\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[ER (TV series)|ER]]''\n| Bennett Cray\n| Episode: \"Somebody to Love\"\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Mobsters (TV series)|Mobsters]]''\n| Narrator\n| Episode: \"Al Capone\"\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[The Simpsons]]''\n| Dr. Robert Terwilliger, Sr.\n| Voice role; episode: \"[[Funeral for a Fiend]]\"\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''[[In Treatment (American TV series)|In Treatment]]''\n| Walter Barnett\n| Recurring role (season 2), 7 episodes\n|-\n| 2009\u20132010\n| ''[[Burn Notice]]''\n| Management\n| Episodes: \"Lesser Evil\", \"Devil You Know\"\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[$h*! My Dad Says|$#*! My Dad Says]]''\n| Lt. Col. Wally Durham\n| Episode: \"The Manly Thing to Do\"\n|-\n| 2011\u20132014\n| ''[[Hot in Cleveland]]''\n| Roy\n| Recurring role (seasons 2\u20133, 5), 6 episodes\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Foyle's War]]''\n| Andrew Del Mar\n| Episode: \"High Castle\"\n|}\n\n==Accolades==\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Award\n!Category\n!Nominated work\n!Result\n!Ref.\n|-\n|1986 \n|[[Tony Award]]\n|[[Tony Award for Best Featured Actor in a Play|Featured Actor in a Play]]\n|''[[The House of Blue Leaves]]''\n|{{win}}\n|<ref>https://www.npr.org/2018/02/09/584509987/remembering-john-mahoney-the-tony-award-winning-actor-and-frasier-star</ref>\n|-\n|1999\n|rowspan=2|[[Primetime Emmy Award]]\n|rowspan=2|[[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Supporting Actor in a Comedy Series|Supporting Actor in a Comedy Series]]\n|rowspan=14|''[[Frasier]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|rowspan=2|<ref>https: