acy.com/obituaries/postgazette/obituary.aspx?pid=192848452 William Gompers]</ref>\n** [[Bob Zeman]], 82, player and coach<ref>[https://www.denverbroncos.com/news/remembering-former-broncos-player-coach-bob-zeman Remembering Bob Zeman, former Broncos assistant coach and All-AFL safety]</ref>\n* [[May 4]] - [[MacArthur Lane]], 77, player<ref>[https://profootballtalk.nbcsports.com/2019/05/06/former-pro-bowl-running-back-macarthur-lane-dies-at-77/ Former Pro Bowl running back MacArthur Lane dies at 77]</ref>\n* [[May 6]] - [[Jimmy Satterfield]], coach (b. [[1939]])<ref>[https://www.thestate.com/sports/high-school/prep-football/article230103674.html SC football coaching legend Jimmy Satterfield dies]</ref>\n* [[May 10]] - [[Dick Tomey]], coach (b. [[1938]])<ref>[https://www.abc15.com/sports/former-arizona-wildcats-football-coach-dick-tomey-passes-away-after-battle-with-lung-cancer Former Arizona Wildcats football coach Dick Tomey passes away after battle with lung cancer]</ref>\n* [[May 16]] - [[Bob Schloredt]], player and coach (b. [[1939]])<ref>[https://komonews.com/sports/huskies/uw-husky-legend-bob-schloredt-passes-away-at-79 UW Husky legend, Bob Schloredt, passes away at 79]</ref>\n* [[May 18]] - [[John Payne (American football)|John Payne]], coach (b. [[1932]])<ref>[https://thompsonfuneral.com/tribute/details/2322/John-Payne/obituary.html Obituary of John David Payne]</ref>\n* [[May 19]] - [[George Chaump]], player and coach (b. [[1935]])<ref>[https://247sports.com/college/ohio-state/Article/Ohio-State-Buckeyes-football-Georga-Chaump-passes-away-at-83-132169686/ Former Ohio State assistant George Chaump passes away at 83]</ref>\n* [[May 23]] - {{interlanguage link|Bill Yoast|de}}, high school coach ([[T. C. Williams High School]]), depicted in ''[[Remember the Titans]]'' (b. [[1924]])<ref>[https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/2019/05/25/bill-yoast-assistant-coach-tc-williams-remember-titans-football-team-dies/ Bill Yoast, assistant coach from T.C. Williams \u2018R